&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Benefits Coordinators Corporation (BCC)&lt;/strong&gt; is a third-party employee benefits administrator and a leader in developing services designed to help our clients run more effective employee benefit programs. We have been experiencing growth and are currently adding a &lt;strong&gt;Benefits Administrator &lt;/strong&gt;to the team. This is a great opportunity to start your career in a role where you can be trained by and work with some of the top experts in the industry.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;In practice, the core activities of the job include:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
