&lt;li&gt;Analyze, interpret, and troubleshoot data across multiple systems to ensure accuracy and resolve discrepancies&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Strengths and skills necessary for success in the role:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Previous experience with Word, Excel, and Outlook will be helpful&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;1–2 years related office experience preferred&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prior benefits experience is preferred, however not required&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong written and oral communication skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong attention to detail paired with the ability to think critically and solve problems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to identify inconsistencies, troubleshoot issues, and work through complex information&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
